Hello and happy to be here!
I have been working in HubSpot for a few years but still feel like a newbie in some areas. Looking forward to learning from you all and sharing the knowledge that I have learned.
What areas are you most interested in learning about?

well recently we have started developing dynamically created pages from HubDB so filtering and getting those pages to read the databases how we need them to has been challenging, so I am looking forward to seeing how others might be doing this. And blog templates, those have always been a bit of a wildcard for me.
